spec_data.Description:
This package contains the firmware for M-Audio/Midiman USB MIDI & Audio devices.

Supported devices:
 - MidiSport 1x1
 - MidiSport 2x2
 - MidiSport 4x4
 - MidiSport 8x8
 - MidiSport Uno
 - Keystation
 - Oxygen
 - Radium

(You do not need a firmware download for the USB Audio Quattro, Duo, or
MidiSport 2x4.)
